{"tid":1804552,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習敗北普京互發新年賀電　習敗北：明年將開啟「中俄科技創新年」","createTime":"2019-12-31T05:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T05:37:10.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"730da17c5b4c09d9f73840ae1ce8c421ecdd1cc8","tid":1804552,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T05:32:14.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平和俄羅斯總統普京互相發新年賀電。<br />\n<br />\n習近平指出，今年是中俄關係發展史上極不平凡的一年，亦是兩國建交70周年，雙方關係邁入新時代。明年將開啟中俄科技創新年，兩國將共同慶祝二戰結束暨聯合國成立75週年。<br />\n<br />\n他說，願意與普京保持密切交往，攜手引領雙邊關係和各領域合作邁上新台階，共同維護多邊主義及國際體系，為中俄發展以及世界增添更多穩定性，注入正能量。<br />\n<br />\n普京表示，兩國之間的協作富有成效，其中俄中東線天然氣管道今年建成並投產通氣，又稱俄方高度重視明年的「俄中科技創新年」，相信在兩國共同努力下，俄中在國際事務中的建設性協作將不斷邁上新台階。<br />\n<br />\n另外，國務院總理李克強同俄羅斯總理梅德韋傑夫也互致新年賀電。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2341037/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2341037%2F&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=f2d218e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2341037/</a>"},{"pid":"90791dd2005104fd787c4b85be9d3b3ac19153d5","tid":1804552,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T05:37:10.000Z","msg":"<ins>德國聯署 </ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=fc2c1666\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=a7da4627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=